import React from 'react'
import Tab from 'react-bootstrap/Tab'
import Tabs from 'react-bootstrap/Tabs'

import StudentLogin from './student-login.component'
import InstructorLogin from './instructor-login.component'

function Card (props) {
  const cardType = props.type === "student" ?
  (
    <Tabs defaultActiveKey={props.defaultTab} id="uncontrolled-tab-example">
      <Tab eventKey="student" title="Student Login">
        <StudentLogin />
      </Tab>
      <Tab eventKey="student" title="Create Student Account" disabled>
        <InstructorLogin />
      </Tab>
    </Tabs>
  )
  : (
    <Tabs defaultActiveKey={props.defaultTab} id="uncontrolled-tab-example">
      <Tab eventKey="student" title="Student">
        <StudentLogin />
      </Tab>
      <Tab eventKey="instructor" title="Instructor" disabled>
        <InstructorLogin />
      </Tab>
    </Tabs>
  )
  return(
   {cardType}
  )
}

export default Card
